One way to visualize it is to think of the particle you want to observe as a croquet ball in motion, and the only way you can "observe" the ball is to whack it with your croquet mallet. Your very observation changes what you see.Perhaps now is a good time to post the link to the What the bleep video that talks about this same thing. Entertaining, informative, and more than a little bit creepy.
