Imagine that you want to measure the frequency of photon at a certain time or point.Frequency is a function of amplitude over time. To measure the frequency accurately you will need to measure it over a certain time, which is likely to mean a certain displacement as well. So you can get a more accurate frequency but the position and time is now more inaccurate.
